# Project Structure

## Directory Layout

```
src/
├── dev/      # Main source files (production code)
└── test/     # Test files and test applications
```

## Guidelines

### `src/dev/` - Source Files
Place all main application code here:
- Application logic
- Components and modules
- Utilities and helpers
- Configuration files
- Build scripts

### `src/test/` - Test Files
Place all testing-related files here:
- Unit tests
- Integration tests
- Test applications
- Test utilities and mocks
- Test fixtures and data

## Examples

```
# ✅ GOOD
src/dev/app.ts
src/dev/utils/helpers.ts
src/test/app.test.ts
src/test/utils/helpers.test.ts

# ❌ BAD
src/app.ts
src/app.test.ts
tests/app.test.ts
```

## When Creating Files

- New feature → `src/dev/`
- Test for that feature → `src/test/` (mirror the path structure)
